'''NBC''', or the '''National Broadcasting Company''' is one of the major television networks in the United States.

NBC is notable in ''[[Star Wars]]'' history for the network television premieres of [[Star Wars: Episode V The Empire Strikes Back|''Star Wars'': Episode V ''The Empire Strikes Back'']] in [[1987]] and [[Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi|''Star Wars'': Episode VI ''Return of the Jedi'']] in [[1989]].

